<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Travio - Solusi Perjalanan Anda</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans">

    <nav class="bg-white shadow-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="#" class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 tracking-wider">TRAVIO</a>
            <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 font-medium">
                <a href="#home" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Beranda</a>
                <a href="#services" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Layanan</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Kontak</a>
            </div>
            <a href="https://wa.me/6285876371055" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-700 transition">Pesan Sekarang</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header id="home" class="relative h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center text-center text-white">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-50 z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-20 px-4">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-4">Jelajahi Dunia Bersama Travio</h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Pengalaman perjalanan tak terlupakan dengan pelayanan terbaik dan harga kompetitif.</p>
            <a href="#services" class="bg-yellow-500 text-gray-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-yellow-400 transition">Lihat Paket Wisata</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="services" class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Layanan Kami</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
                <div class="p-8 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-plane-departure text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Tiket Pesawat</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Pemesanan tiket domestik dan internasional dengan harga transparan.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-hotel text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Pemesanan Hotel</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Pilihan akomodasi mulai dari budget hingga hotel berbintang lima.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Paket Tour</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Paket wisata lengkap yang disusun khusus untuk kenyamanan Anda.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="py-20 bg-gray-100">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row">
                <div class="bg-blue-600 p-10 text-white md:w-1/3">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Hubungi Kami</h2>
                    <p class="mb-8">Kami siap membantu merencanakan liburan impian Anda kapan saja.</p>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope mr-4"></i>
                            <span>temifahmirozi@gmail.com</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-phone mr-4"></i>
                            <span>085876371055</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="p-10 md:w-2/3">
                    <form action="#" class="space-y-4">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Nama Lengkap</label>
                            <input type="text" class="w-full mt-1 p-3 border rounded-lg focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500" placeholder="Masukkan nama Anda">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Pesan</label>
                            <textarea rows="4" class="w-full mt-1 p-3 border rounded-lg focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500" placeholder="Apa yang bisa kami bantu?"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition">Kirim Pesan</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-10">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">TRAVIO</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Partner setia perjalanan Anda mengeksplorasi keindahan dunia.</p>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-800 pt-6">
                <p>&copy; 2023 Travio Travel Agent. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
